{"body": "It seems odd to have to specify the column names in two places. How about we support the following syntax for 1.9 (where hashes are ordered):\r\n\r\n``` ruby\r\nadd_index(:accounts, branch_id: :desc, part_id: :asc)\r\n```\r\n\r\nWith a fallback for 1.8:\r\n\r\n``` ruby\r\nadd_index(:accounts, [[:branch_id, :desc], [:part_id, :asc]])\r\n```\r\n\r\n?", "url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rails/rails/issues/comments/2618904", "created_at": "2011-11-03T15:58:18Z", "html_url": "https://github.com/rails/rails/pull/3351#issuecomment-2618904", "updated_at": "2011-11-03T15:58:18Z", "repo": "rails", "issue_id": 3351, "user": {"following_url": "https://api.github.com/users/jonleighton/following{/other_user}", "events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/jonleighton/events{/privacy}", "organizations_url": "https://api.github.com/users/jonleighton/orgs", "url": "https://api.github.com/users/jonleighton", "gists_url": "https://api.github.com/users/jonleighton/gists{/gist_id}", "html_url": "https://github.com/jonleighton", "subscriptions_url": "https://api.github.com/users/jonleighton/subscriptions", "avatar_url": "https://0.gravatar.com/avatar/2940bc7d4506f3e099e3dcc32a412b98?d=https%3A%2F%2Fidenticons.github.com%2F798cebccb32617ad94123450fd137104.png", "repos_url": "https://api.github.com/users/jonleighton/repos", "received_events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/jonleighton/received_events", "gravatar_id": "2940bc7d4506f3e099e3dcc32a412b98", "starred_url": "https://api.github.com/users/jonleighton/starred{/owner}{/repo}", "login": "jonleighton", "type": "User", "id": 1979, "followers_url": "https://api.github.com/users/jonleighton/followers"}, "owner": "rails", "_id": {"$oid": "52383744bd3543c15100fe3a"}, "id": 2618904, "issue_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rails/rails/issues/3351"}
